reqBody.prompt: A magical girl, a guardian of light. Long, flowing brown hair, she has stylized, minimalist, anime-inspired eyes that are large and expressive with simplified details, focusing on conveying emotion through shape and limited shading. She wears a flowing, magical girl outfit with a color palette of white, gold, and deep blue and dress boots. She is standing with her arms outstretched to the sides, palms facing downwards, and her legs slightly apart with a slight bend in her knees. Reference sheet. Deep black background.
